  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive hell in this Roguelike Deckbuilder that features card battles with an in-depth auto-battler-esque synergy and combo system. Help Bobo, our little penguin, recruit allies and face the many horrors that await him on his journey to save his friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3532340/extras/356dd1e4e720490f3884ee990b087b90.avif?t=1774065206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3532340/extras_big/356dd1e4e720490f3884ee990b087b90.avif?t=1774065206 width=800 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit powerful allies and create your <strong>team composition</strong> navigating an in-depth synergy system! Arrange powerful<strong> </strong>combinations to exploit and escalate your power level to cruise through the gates of hell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3532340/extras/b650812fa56c7dc6eeced090971b9b8d.avif?t=1774065206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3532340/extras_big/b650812fa56c7dc6eeced090971b9b8d.avif?t=1774065206 width=800 height=87 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relinquish your foes and pick up <strong>powerful items</strong> to fine-tune your <strong>composition</strong>. Carefully weigh the pros and cons of each artifact and use unique interactions to give you the edge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3532340/extras/25a486b4889c074b7c3c971f27e811e4.avif?t=1774065206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3532340/extras_big/25a486b4889c074b7c3c971f27e811e4.avif?t=1774065206 width=800 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find your way through the circles of hell under the guidance of our local, friendly red-hooded figure. Beware of your <strong>choices</strong>, penguin, as decision-making is the deciding factor between facing the unpleasant and the unrelenting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3532340/extras/b1c75420186903367e99ad81060afcf1.avif?t=1774065206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3532340/extras_big/b1c75420186903367e99ad81060afcf1.avif?t=1774065206 width=800 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bobo In Hell at release will ship with: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >165+ character cards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ unique items.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ action cards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20+ unique enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20+ synergetic archetypes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hundreds of different viable builds and combinations.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive hell in this Roguelike Deckbuilder that features card battles with an in-depth auto-battler-esque synergy and combo system. Help Bobo, our little penguin, recruit allies and face the many horrors that await him on his journey to save his friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3532340/extras/356dd1e4e720490f3884ee990b087b90.avif?t=1774065206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3532340/extras_big/356dd1e4e720490f3884ee990b087b90.avif?t=1774065206 width=800 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit powerful allies and create your <strong>team composition</strong> navigating an in-depth synergy system! Arrange powerful<strong> </strong>combinations to exploit and escalate your power level to cruise through the gates of hell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3532340/extras/b650812fa56c7dc6eeced090971b9b8d.avif?t=1774065206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3532340/extras_big/b650812fa56c7dc6eeced090971b9b8d.avif?t=1774065206 width=800 height=87 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relinquish your foes and pick up <strong>powerful items</strong> to fine-tune your <strong>composition</strong>. Carefully weigh the pros and cons of each artifact and use unique interactions to give you the edge.</p><p class=\